Button Configuration : 
player 1 :
-move left : left button
-move right : right button
-attack : L
-guard : K
-skill : O

player 2:
-move left : A
-move right : D
-attack : G
-guard : F
-skill : R

Choose options in Map with left and right and Enter
Escape to go back from city

==============================================================================WEEK 1 IMPLEMENTATION===================================================================
Implementation : -Add Model of characters (monster and hero), city, shop, item
				 -Some functions in Battlefield
				 -Attack functions for characters
Testing : Automatic Testing (src/test)

